stats.headline: Statistics
stats.subheadline: This is important stats that you should know

data.title: Total Supply
data.tooltip: Total Supply of the token includes the circulating supply and the tokens that are locked or burned.

data.title: Circulating Supply
data.tooltip: Circulating supply of the token is the amount of tokens that are in circulation in the market. This does not include the tokens that are locked or burned.

data.title: Swap Threshold
data.tooltip: Swap Threshold is the amount of tokens that are required to be swapped before the swapback is enabled. This is to prevent the swap from being enabled too early and causing a dump.

data.title: Trade Enabled
data.tooltip: Trade enable is wether the token is enabled for trading yet (can only be enabled and never be disabled). If this is disabled, the token cannot be traded yet.

data.title: Swap Enabled
data.tooltip: Swap enabled is wether the swapback is enabled or disabled.

data.title: Fee Active
data.tooltip: Fee active is wether the fee is active or disabled. If this is disabled, the fee will not be collected.

data.title: Total Auto Buyback
data.tooltip: Total Auto Buyback is the amount of tokens that are bought back automatically by the contract.

data.title: Total Fee Collected
data.tooltip: Total Fee Collected is the amount of tokens that are collected as fee.

data.title: Collected Burn Fee
data.tooltip: Collected Burn Fee is the amount of tokens that are collected as burn fee.

data.title: Collected Marketing Fee
data.tooltip: Collected Marketing Fee is the amount of tokens that are collected as marketing fee.

data.title: Collected Staking Fee
data.tooltip: Collected Staking Fee is the amount of tokens that are collected as staking fee.

data.title: Total Fee Redeemed
data.tooltip: Total Fee Redeemed is the amount of tokens that are redeemed from the contract.

data.title: Redeemed Burn Fee
data.tooltip: Redeemed Burn Fee is the amount of tokens that are redeemed as burn fee.

data.title: Redeemed Marketing Fee
data.tooltip: Redeemed Marketing Fee is the amount of tokens that are redeemed as marketing fee.

data.title: Redeemed Staking Fee
data.tooltip: Redeemed Staking Fee is the amount of tokens that are redeemed as staking fee.
